<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>杯子蛋糕糕實驗室</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.5/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Xe+8cL9oJa6tN/veChSP7q+mnSPaj5Bcu9mPX5F5xIGE0DVittaqT5lorf0EI7Vk"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ODmDIVzN+pFdexxHEHFBQH3/9/vQ9uori45z4JjnFsRydbmQbmL5t1tQ0culUzyK"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: rgb(255, 225, 201);
        }
        .animate__animated:hover{
            animation-iteration-count : infinite
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid" style="margin-top: 107px;">
        <nav class="fixed-top navbar navbar-expand-lg nav nav-tabs" style="background-color: burlywood;" role="tablist">
            <div class="flex-grow-0 ms-3">
                <img src="./_image/首頁圖.png" class="active animate__animated animate__zoomIn" alt="Logo" width="90px"
                    id="home-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#home" type="button" role="tab"
                    aria-controls="home" aria-selected="true">
            </div>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse " id="navbarSupportedContent" style="background-color: burlywood;">
                <div class="flex-grow-1"><img class="nav-link m-auto" id="comics-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                        data-bs-target="#comics" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="comics" aria-selected="false"
                        src="/_image/漫畫標題.png" width="90%"> </div>
                <div class="flex-grow-1"><img class="nav-link m-auto" id="video-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                        data-bs-target="#video" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="video" aria-selected="false"
                        src="/_image/YT標題.png" width="90%"></div>
                <div class="flex-grow-1"><img class="nav-link m-auto" calss id="Line_stick-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab"
                        data-bs-target="#Line_stick" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="Line_stick"
                        aria-selected="false" src="/_image/LINE標題.png" width="90%" href="#"></div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="tab-content">
            <div class="tab-pane fade show active " id="home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="home-tab" tabindex="0">
                <div class="d-grid d-lg-flex align-items-center border border-2 border-light w-75 container pt-1 mb-2">
                    <div class="flex-grow-0 text-center"><img src="/_image/首頁圖.png" type="button" id="comics-tab2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 ">
                        <p class="h4 ">
                            Hi~ Hi~ 大家好!我是杯子蛋糕糕，興趣是畫輕鬆可愛的漫畫，還有挑戰做各種各樣的羊毛氈~
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="d-grid d-lg-flex align-items-center border border-2 border-light w-75 container pt-1 mb-2">
                    <div class="flex-grow-0 text-center"><img src="/_image/首頁圖.png" type="button" id="video-tab2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 ">
                        <p class="h4 ">從奇妙糕糕星來地球修行的杯子蛋糕糕。
                            使用戳針為魔法棒，羊毛為魔法材料，變出一個又一個可愛的小夥伴!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="d-grid d-lg-flex align-items-center border border-2 border-light w-75 container pt-1 mb-2">
                    <div class="flex-grow-0 text-center"><img src="/_image/首頁圖.png" type="button" id="Line_stick-tab2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-grow-1 ">
                        <p class="h4 ">
                            可愛又搞怪的杯子蛋糕糕初登場，為您獻上各種活潑生動的表情~
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade " id="comics" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="comics-tab" tabindex="0">
                <div class="d-grid d-lg-flex border border-5 text-center w-75 container pt-1">
                    <div class="flex-grow-1"><img src="/_image/漫畫封面.jpg"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="video" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="video-tab" tabindex="0">
                <div class="flex-grow-1 mx-1 mb-1"><img src="/_image/YT_.png" class="img-fluid"></div>
                <div class=" text-center container  ratio ratio-4x3">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xtot61Fx434?si=FlYdExi62X4CRSnI"
                        title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="Line_stick" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="Line_stick-tab" tabindex="0">
                <div class="d-grid d-lg-flex text-center container pt-1">
                    <div class="flex-grow-1"><img src="/_image/LINE標題.png" width="100%"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-block text-center w-75 container pt-1">
                    <div><img src="/_image/貼圖_1.png" width="200px"><img src="/_image/貼圖_2.png"
                            width="200px"><img src="/_image/貼圖_3.png" width="200px"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fixed-bottom text-end m-4"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/CakekeCup"><img
                        src="/_image/首頁圖.png" width="50px" class="animate__animated" id="bottom_img"></a></div>
            <div class="header container" style="margin-top: 200px;">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <h1 class="my-4">留言板</h1>
                    <button class="btn btn-success mb-4" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#exampleModal">發表留言</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="comments container mb-4">
                <% dataList.forEach(function(dataList) { %>
                    <ul class="list-group bg-transparent">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">
                            <div class="d-flex flex-column bg-transparent">
                                <div class="mb-3 d-flex">
                                    <span class="font-weight-bold me-2 h4">
                                        <%= dataList['message_title'] %>
                                    </span>
                                    <small class="ms-auto ">
                                        <%= dataList['message_date'] %>
                                    </small>
                                </div>
                                <span class="mb-3">
                                    <%= dataList['message_text'] %>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <% }); %>
            </div>
            <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content" style="background-color: antiquewhite;">
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">新增留言</h1>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            <form method="post" action="/message_board/post">
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="recipient_name" class="col-form-label">名稱/標題</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="recipient_name">
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="message_text" class="col-form-label">內容</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" name="message_text"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="modal-footer">
                                    <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                        value="送出"></input>
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">取消</button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            $(document).ready(function () {
                $('#comics-tab2').on('click', () => {
                    $("#comics-tab").click();
                });
                $('#video-tab2').on('click', () => {
                    $("#video-tab").click();
                });
                $('#Line_stick-tab2').on('click', () => {
                    $("#Line_stick-tab").click();
                });
            })
            $('.nav-link,#home-tab').on('click', function () {
                window.scrollTo(0, 0);
            })
            $("#home-tab,#bottom_img").mouseenter(function () {
                $(this).removeClass('animate__zoomIn')
                $(this).addClass('animate__pulse')
            })
            // $("#bottom_img").mouseenter(function () {
            //     $(this).addClass('animate__pulse')
            // })
        </script>
</body>

</html>